Where to Watch

Howard Stern sidekick, actor-comedian Artie Lange, stars in and cowrote this winning slob comedy about the epic softball battles between two archrival teams in a New Jersey bar league. Because of their many on-field base-brawls, officials decide that only the squad that wins the championship can come back and compete the next year, and that raises the already high stakes. Directed and cowritten by Frank Sebastiano. Cara Buono, Ralph Macchio. Also known as "Artie Lange's Beer League."
